trans-unit.source: is an open-source YouTube downloader built under Google's Material Design specifications. You can seamlessly download your favorite videos as video or audio files, and even subscribe to your favorite channels and playlists to keep updated with their new videos.
trans-unit.target: on avoimen koodin YouTube-tallennusohjelma, joka on tehty Googlen Material Design -vaatimusten mukaisesti. Voit saumattomasti tallentaa suosikkivideosi videona tai äänenä. Voit jopa tilata suosikkikanaviasi ja soittolistojasi pysyäksesi ajan tasalla heidän uusista videoista.

trans-unit.source: has some awesome features included! An extensive API, Docker support, and localization (translation) support. Read up on all the supported features by clicking on the GitHub icon above.
